What is the output?
```dart
for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
  if (i == 2) continue;
  print(i);
}
```

slides.codeSnippet:
void main() {
  for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
    if (i % 2 == 0) continue; // skip even numbers
    print('Odd: $i');
    if (i > 7) break;          // stop after 7
  }
}
